US government debt, EU government debt, Japan government debt.. Those who think that this is bad will be surprised to learn a simple trick: public debt servicing 0.5% per year; inflation 7.5% per year. 34 years of such mathematics and the relative size of public debt will shrink by 10 times even without any repayment.. It is enough for the government to raise the minimum wages, benefits, child allowances to keep inflation going. But Russia has practically no public debt ..